milestones.description: David Gower has become the top scorer for ENG in ODIs with 1198 runs, going past Geoff Boycott's 1082
David Gower's 158 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for ENG), surpassing Dennis Amiss's 137
David Gower has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (96) in an innings in ODIs for ENG, going past Dennis Amiss's 72
Derek Randall and David Gower's 113-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 110 between Mike Gatting and David Gower
Hadlee and Gary Troup's 63-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 37 between Dayle Hadlee and Lance Cairns
Hadlee and Gary Troup's 63-run partnership is the highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Syed Abid Ali
This is the highest match aggregate (480) involving teams England & New Zealand in ODIs
David Gower has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (96) in an innings in ODIs, going past Viv Richards's 86
